      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this showroom-ready masterpiece. Meticulously preserved and presenting in unrivaled condition, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a standard of care that is second to none. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a testament to precision engineering and dedicated stewardship. Available now for those who refuse to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
