      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014always kept under a cover and polished to a mirror finish. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated with nothing but love and is ready for the open road, you've found it! Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a surgically clean, driver-focused E46 M3. The S54 power plant features a bulletproofed top end with a complete Besian VANOS system and treated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and long-term reliability. The chassis has been fully reinforced to eliminate the common subframe fatigue, paired with a custom-valved coilover setup for razor-sharp turn-in and neutral handling. Transmission shifts are notched and precise, benefiting from a weighted selector rod and fresh performance-grade fluids. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized specimen with zero parasitic loss and a throttle response that puts modern drive-by-wire systems to shame. Truly a turn-key, investment-grade machine maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless finish. Showroom interior. Zero mechanical issues. It\u2019s mint and it\u2019s priced to move. Don't wait.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
