      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour, the wind rushing past as you glide down a coastal highway in this automotive masterpiece. Every curve of its hand-polished silhouette tells a story of elegance and timeless grace. The engine doesn't just start; it awakens with a soulful hum that promises endless horizons. Inside, the scent of heritage leather and the cool touch of chrome transport you to an era where driving was an art form. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved moment of perfection, waiting for a driver who understands that some legends never fade.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom-fresh condition. This specimen has been curated with exacting standards, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every surface reflects meticulous care, and its mechanical performance is absolute. For the discerning driver who demands nothing short of excellence, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Experience the confidence of a car that looks and drives as though it just departed the assembly line.",
      "price": 47900.0,
