    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It breaks my heart a little to say goodbye, but it\u2019s time for my pride and joy to find a new home. This beauty is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch stayed pristine. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that's been truly loved, come take a look\u2014I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
