    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a specimen-grade example of automotive engineering. This chassis has been maintained to a standard that exceeds factory tolerances, with every fluid service utilizing high-viscosity synthetics to ensure optimal shear stability and internal component longevity. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, showing zero signs of eccentric shaft wear, while the forced induction system holds peak boost with surgical precision. The suspension geometry has been corner-balanced with adjustable dampers for neutral turn-in and maximum mechanical grip. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a recalibrated masterpiece of thermal efficiency and drivetrain rigidity. For the buyer who understands parasitic loss and demands a zero-lash driving experience, this is the definitive choice.",
